  "translations": {
    "en": "So Yusuf said: 'Enter Egypt, God willing, in security.' And he raised his parents upon the throne, and they fell down in prostration to him. And Yusuf said to Ya'qub: 'O my father, this is the interpretation of my dream of before. My Lord has made it reality' -- until His saying -- 'cause me to die as a Muslim and join me with the righteous.'",
